author: cbs8
title: Saucier woman dies in single vehicle crash
text:
SAUCIER, Miss. (AP) - Authorities say a 72-year-old Saucier woman died when the pickup she was driving ran off the road and struck a utility pole and a tree.
Harrison County Coroner Gary Hargrove said Mary Waltman died Sunday from blunt force trauma.
Hargrove said Waltman failed to negotiate a curve on Saucier Lizana Road.
He says she was wearing a seatbelt.
